        <h3><a href="/questions/531360/raid-10-3-drives-or-2-drives" class="question-hyperlink">RAID 10, 3 drives or 2 drives?</a></h3>
        <div class="excerpt">
            Drives are very cheap these days.  Would it be worth it to increase the group size from 2 to 3.  I found 1TB drives for $60.  I feel as if the array is very vulnerable to failure in a 2 group setup ...
        </div>          
        <div class="tags t-raid t-storage t-best-practices">
            <a href="/questions/tagged/raid" class="post-tag" title="show questions tagged &#39;raid&#39;" rel="tag">raid</a> <a href="/questions/tagged/storage" class="post-tag" title="show questions tagged &#39;storage&#39;" rel="tag">storage</a> <a href="/questions/tagged/best-practices" class="post-tag" title="show questions tagged &#39;best-practices&#39;" rel="tag">best-practices</a> 

            <div class="post-menu">
                                                            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="started fr">
            <div class="user-info ">
    <div class="user-action-time">
        asked <span title="2013-08-15 21:50:48Z" class="relativetime">Aug 15 '13 at 21:50</span>
    </div>
    <div class="user-gravatar32">
        <a href="/users/185795/oooooo3333"><div><img src="https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/2ebb635ae993fe3393e7ef212fdd4010?s=32&d=identicon&r=PG" alt="" width="32" height="32"></div></a>
    </div>
